description.narrative: 2019 saw changes to management in the Ministry of Public Health at central level as well at regional level following a change in government. The organizational structure of the Ministry also changed with the reorganization of programmes. UNICEF provided technical and financial support for the development of strategic documents reflecting the new vision. Support focused on the following elements: strategic planning; steering committee reorganization; advocacy for better use of public funds; community health platform development; and health system strengthening platform establishment to improve coordination. | Status:Constrained | As-of Date:31/12/2019
